title: Topher Grace
itunes:title: Topher Grace
description:
Whitney’s old friend Topher Grace comes on the show to reminisce and tell everyone how her first stand up set went twenty years ago.  He also talks about his new ABC show Home Economics and tells us how he knew his wife was the one.  We also FaceTime his co-star  Sasheer Zamata!  You know and love Topher Grace from That 70's Show, BlacKkKlansman, Traffic, and countless other fabulous performances.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
